Title: Bodenmiller_BCR_XL_SE
Description: Mass cytometry data from Bodenmiller et al. (2012). Paired samples of healthy PBMCs, where one sample from each pair was stimulated with B cell receptor / Fc receptor cross-linker (BCR-XL). This dataset can be used to benchmark algorithms for differential analysis.

Title: Bodenmiller_BCR_XL_flowSet
Description: Mass cytometry data from Bodenmiller et al. (2012). Paired samples of healthy PBMCs, where one sample from each pair was stimulated with B cell receptor / Fc receptor cross-linker (BCR-XL). This dataset can be used to benchmark algorithms for differential analysis.

Title: Levine_32dim_SE
Description: 32-dimensional mass cytometry (CyTOF) dataset from Levine et al. (2015), containing 14 manually gated immune cell populations from healthy human bone marrow mononuclear cells (BMMCs). This dataset can be used to benchmark clustering algorithms.

Title: Levine_32dim_flowSet
Description: 32-dimensional mass cytometry (CyTOF) dataset from Levine et al. (2015), containing 14 manually gated immune cell populations from healthy human bone marrow mononuclear cells (BMMCs). This dataset can be used to benchmark clustering algorithms.

Title: Levine_13dim_SE
Description: 13-dimensional mass cytometry (CyTOF) dataset from Levine et al. (2015), containing 24 manually gated immune cell populations from healthy human bone marrow mononuclear cells (BMMCs). This dataset can be used to benchmark clustering algorithms.

Title: Levine_13dim_flowSet
Description: 13-dimensional mass cytometry (CyTOF) dataset from Levine et al. (2015), containing 24 manually gated immune cell populations from healthy human bone marrow mononuclear cells (BMMCs). This dataset can be used to benchmark clustering algorithms.
